          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use this property to update the size of the collection view’s content area. The default value of this property is ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coregraphics/cgsizezero",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". Changing the value causes the collection view to add the specified height and width values to its ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UIScrollView/contentSize",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " property. Thus, positive values grow the content area and negative values shrink it.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
